conversation.content: Namaste! Main Triotech ki Sales Assistant hoon.  Main aapki kis tarah help kar sakti hoon?
I am Anika, from jamtech, i want to know about xeny, please share my info with sales team I want to connect with them

Welcome Anika ji from Jamtech!  Xeny ke bare mein jaanne ke liye aapne contact kiya, yeh badi baat hai!  Xeny humara ek powerful AI-powered solution hai jo aapke business ko automate karne mein madad karega.

Toh, aapke liye Xeny kitna relevant hai, yeh samajhne ke liye, mujhe kuch aur details chahiyen.  Please share your email address and phone number.  Aur bataiye ki aapke budget ka kya hai?  Isse hum aapko sahi solution suggest kar payenge.
my email: anika@jamtech.in, phone number:6523658941, Budget: 500000,

Anika ji,  aapne apna email, phone number aur budget share kiya,  yeh aapki taraf se bahut achcha response hai!   Ab sirf ek baat baki hai: aap Xeny ko apne business ke kis specific area mein use karna chahti hain?   Yeh jaanne se hum aapko aur zyada customize solution de sakte hain.  Iske baad main aapki details hamari sales team ke saath share kar dungi. Kya main aapki details share kar sakti hun?
Okay Anika ji.  Sharing your details now...

Shukriya Anika ji!  Aapki details hamari sales team ke saath share kar di gayi hain.  Wo aapse jaldi contact karenge Xeny ke bare mein aur aapke business ki specific requirements ko samajhne ke liye.  Dhanyawad!
